title: Jim Jones Interview and More
itunes:title: Jim Jones Interview and More
description:
Thursday 12/6 - Today on the show we had Jim Jones stop by where he spoke about solo project called "Wasted Talent", dipset and lets just say he had a message for Mase after the Mase and Cam'ron beef. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to three guys that broke into a home, and got caught while police were investigating the home. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
